Package biz.gabrys.lesscss.compiler

The LessCSS Compiler compiles Less source files to the CSS code.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    LessCompiler
    Responsible for compiling Less sources to the CSS code.
    OperatingSystemChecker
    Responsible for checking operating system.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CompilerOptions
    Options that control the Less compilation process.
    CompilerOptionsBuilder
    Responsible for creating new instances of the CompilerOptions which are compatible with version 1.7.5.
    IOUtils
    Provides tools for working with I/O.
    LessCompilerImpl
    Default implementation of the LessCompiler.
    ListWithoutEmptyValuesBuilder
    Responsible for creating new instances of the List which stores not empty values.
    OperatingSystemCheckerImpl
    Default implementation of the OperatingSystemChecker based on the system properties.
    StringUtils
    Provides functionality for working with texts.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CompilerException
    Thrown to indicate that an error occurred during compilation process.
    InitializationException
    Thrown to indicate that an error occurred during compiler initialization.
    ResolveImportException
    Thrown to indicate that an error occurred while resolving imports.
    SyntaxException
    Thrown to indicate that a syntax error occurred during source file compilation.

Package biz.gabrys.lesscss.compiler Description
